box                     Build a bounding box
code_bbox               Get the code to reproduce your bounding box
manual_bbox             Manually build a bounding box using the Shiny
                        rectangle
morph                   Morph the format of a bounding box
to_word_str             Morph any bounding box to a word string
                        bounding box
word_str_to_xy_matrix   Morph an xy string bbox to a xy matrix bbox
word_str_to_xy_str      Morph a word string bbox to a xy string bbox
